sequenceDiagram
    title Odoo Administrative Onboarding & Data Synchronization Flow

    participant HR as HR Manager / System Admin
    participant AdminMod as Administrative<br/>Management Module
    participant AuthProv as External<br/>Authentication Provider
    participant AccessMod as Access Rights &<br/>Groups Module
    participant DataEngine as Data Import/<br/>Export Engine
    participant AuditMod as Logging &<br/>Audit Tracking
    participant Auditor as Compliance<br/>Auditor
    participant ExtTool as External<br/>Data Tool

    %% 1. User Creation & Invitation
    HR->>AdminMod: Create new user<br/>(Name, Email, Company)
    activate AdminMod
    AdminMod->>AuthProv: Send invitation email<br/>(with setup link)
    AuthProv-->>AdminMod: Acknowledge
    AdminMod-->>HR: User record created
    deactivate AdminMod

    %% 2. Assign Access Rights
    HR->>AccessMod: Assign user to groups<br/>(e.g., Sales/User, HR/Officer)
    activate AccessMod
    AccessMod->>AccessMod: Apply model permissions<br/>+ record rules (e.g., by company)
    AccessMod-->>HR: Access rights updated
    deactivate AccessMod

    %% 3. Bulk Data Import
    HR->>DataEngine: Upload CSV (Contacts, Products)
    activate DataEngine
    DataEngine->>DataEngine: Validate fields & auth scope
    DataEngine->>DataEngine: Create/update records<br/>(respecting access rules)
    DataEngine-->>HR: Import successful
    deactivate DataEngine

    %% 4. Data Export for Audit
    Auditor->>DataEngine: Request export<br/>(e.g., user list, transactions)
    activate DataEngine
    DataEngine->>DataEngine: Filter by userâ€™s access rights
    DataEngine->>ExtTool: Deliver CSV/Excel file
    ExtTool-->>Auditor: Data received
    deactivate DataEngine

    %% 5. Audit Logging
    activate AuditMod
    AdminMod->>AuditMod: Log: "User created"
    AccessMod->>AuditMod: Log: "Groups assigned"
    DataEngine->>AuditMod: Log: "Data imported/exported"
    deactivate AuditMod

    Auditor->>AuditMod: Query audit logs<br/>(Who changed what?)
    activate AuditMod
    AuditMod-->>Auditor: Return activity timeline<br/>(User, Timestamp, Action, IP)
    deactivate AuditMod